name: HyperlinkPageItemSources

properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

methods.name: add
methods.description: Creates a new hyperlink page item source.

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.description: Initial values for properties of the new HyperlinkPageItemSource (Optional)

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the HyperlinkPageItemSource.

methods.name: item
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkPageItemSource with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

methods.name: itemByName
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkPageItemSource with the specified name.

methods.name: itemByID
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkPageItemSource with the specified ID.

methods.name: itemByRange
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkPageItemSources within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: The HyperlinkPageItemSource, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: HyperlinkPageItemSource, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: The HyperlinkPageItemSource, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: HyperlinkPageItemSource, Long Integer or String.

methods.name: firstItem
methods.description: Returns the first HyperlinkPageItemSource in the collection.

methods.name: lastItem
methods.description: Returns the last HyperlinkPageItemSource in the collection.

methods.name: middleItem
methods.description: Returns the middle HyperlinkPageItemSource in the collection.

methods.name: previousItem
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkPageItemSource with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the HyperlinkPageItemSource that follows the desired HyperlinkPageItemSource.

methods.name: nextItem
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkPageItemSource whose index follows the specified HyperlinkPageItemSource in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The HyperlinkPageItemSource whose index comes before the desired HyperlinkPageItemSource.

methods.name: anyItem
methods.description: Returns any HyperlinkPageItemSource in the collection.

methods.name: everyItem
